<p>Until 1994, he served as the general manager, chair of the board of directors or the founder of various industrial and financial institutions and commercial banks inside and outside Turkey. After 1994, he has been involved in education and civil society activities inside and outside the country and has been in their management. He is among the founders of Enka Schools and Community Volunteers Foundation (TOG). He still undertakes voluntary responsibilities such as a member of the board of directors, member of the board of trustees, member of the supervisory board in many associations and foundations, and also serves as a member of the board of directors in various industrial companies. He is one of the founders of the Sen De Gel association and is currently the chair of the association's board of directors.</p>